<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://unpkg.com/@jarstone/dselect/dist/css/dselect.css"
    />

    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="info.css" />

    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      integrity="sha384-rbsA2VBKQhggwzxH7pPCaAqO46MgnOM80zW1RWuH61DGLwZJEdK2Kadq2F9CUG65"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />

    <script src="https://unpkg.com/maplibre-gl@2.4.0/dist/maplibre-gl.js"></script>
    <link
      href="https://unpkg.com/maplibre-gl@2.4.0/dist/maplibre-gl.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <title>The World Data</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gradiente-vice-city">
    <%- include('header'); %>

    <h2 class="main_title mt-5 text-light">The World API.</h2>
    <p class="text-center text text-light my-4 fs-6">
      Hola y bienvenido, est치 api te proporciona una lista de todos,los pa칤ses
      del mundo con sus respectivos estados o regiones adem치s de sus ciudades o
      pueblos. Esto es solo una demo de lo que se puede hacer con estos datos.
      API publica creada por
      <a href="https://github.com/JoanCermeno" blank_ class="text-light"
        ><b> Joan Cerme침o</b></a
      >
    </p>

    <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center">
      <span class="text-center text-light fs-1">{游깵}</span>
    </div>

    <div class="container w-75 py-2 border rounded bg-light">
      <div
        class="container d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center text-center"
      >
        <h2 class="font-monospace">Ejemplo</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="form-floating mx-auto p-2">
        <select
          class="form-select form-select-sm"
          id="select_pais"
          aria-label="Default select example"
        >
          <option selected value="default">Selecciona un pais</option>
          <% paises.forEach(function(pais) { %>
          <option value="<%= pais.id %>"><%= pais.name %></option>
          <% }); %>
        </select>
        <label for="select_pais"
          >Pais
          <div class="bar-load hiden" id="bar-load-estado">
            <div class="bar-padding"></div>
          </div>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="form-floating p-2">
        <select
          class="form-select form-select-sm"
          id="select_estado"
          aria-label="Default select example"
        >
          <option selected value="default">Selecciona un Estado</option>
        </select>

        <label for="select_estado"
          >Estados
          <div class="bar-load hiden" id="bar-load-estado">
            <div class="bar-padding"></div>
          </div>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="form-floating p-2">
        <select
          class="form-select form-select-sm"
          id="select_ciudad"
          aria-label="Default select example"
        >
          <option selected value="default">Selecione una Ciudad</option>
        </select>
        <label for="select_ciudad">
          Ciudades
          <div class="bar-load hiden" id="bar-load-ciudad">
            <div class="bar-padding"></div>
          </div>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="container mx-auto" style="width: 200px">
        <button type="button" id="btnGetInfo" class="btn btn-outline-info">
          Solicitar informaci칩n
        </button>
      </div>

      <section
        class="container d-none d-flex flex-column align-items-center mt-5"
        id="section-map"
      >
        <article
          class="container alert alert-dark"
          id="article_description"
          role="alert"
        >
          <div class="bar-load hiden" id="bar-load-metada">
            <div class="bar-padding"></div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div
          class="hiden mx-auto mb-5"
          id="map"
          style="width: 400px; height: 300px"
        ></div>

        <section
          id="bottom-container-map"
          class="container d-flex justify-content-evenly alert alert-info"
          role="alert"
        >
          <span class="badge text-bg-info text-light" id="badge-lng"></span>
          <span class="badge text-bg-info text-light" id="badge-lat"></span>
        </section>
      </section>
    </div>
    <footer></footer>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/selectSearch.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/showMap.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/reqWikipedia.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
